            <h2>Republic Airways Refund Policy</h2>
            <p>Republic Airways is a carrier airline that operates both domestic and international flights. Frequent flyer programs are available on Republic Airlines. Those who intend to travel with Republic Airways can book their tickets both online and by phoning the airline's reservation number. </p>

            <h2>Refund Policy</h2>

            <p>Republic Airlines provides the convenience of canceling flights online. Passengers can also get a refund by visiting Republic Airways' official website and filling out the refund request form. Only qualifying Republic Airways <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/">flight tickets</a> that are canceled during the active time are eligible for a refund. You will be charged between $200 and $500 to cancel a non-refundable ticket, based on the flight duration, location, and fare class. The remaining price will be issued as an e-Credit for use on a<a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/republic-airlines.aspx"> Republic Airlines flight</a> in the future. </p>

            <h2>FAQs</h2>

            <h3>How can I cancel my flight ticket with Republic airways?</h3>
            <p>If you want to cancel your reserved ticket with Republic Airlines, you can do it in two ways. Online as well as by Telephone cancellation facility is available for the passengers. To begin the cancellation process, have your flight confirmation number ready to enter or present to the aviation executive. You will be informed of the refund alternatives available once the Republic Airlines cancellation process is completed. </p>
            <h3>When can I request a refund? When can I expect it? </h3>
            <p>After your refund request is approved, the payment will be executed within 7-10 working days. If there are any cancellation charges, they will be applied and the remaining payment will be credited to the same payment method which was used at the time of the booking. 24-hour free cancellation facility is also available for the customers. </p>
            <h3>Can I ask for compensation if my flight gets delayed by 2 hours? </h3>
            <p>A canceled flight automatically creates a frustrating mood and journey and holds up your further plans. So, in such a case getting compensation becomes your right because it entirely becomes the responsibility of Republic Airways. </p>
            <h3>How to check if my flight is refundable? </h3>
            <p>Visit Republic Airlines' website to check if the flight ticket is refundable or not. Enter the ticket number and instantly the refund eligibility and data will be shown on the screen. If in case the ticket is not refundable, a passenger can cancel his/her journey and use the cost to book a Republic Airways flight in the future. </p>
            <h3>What is the best way to see if my airline is refundable? </h3>
            <p>Read the terms and conditions of the refund policy carefully. Check the reimbursement section to see if a full refund or a partial refund is available. When your preferred airlines allow partial refunds, users can browse for fully refundable plane tickets. You will get complete information about when the cancellation charges are taken and when not so that you can get your amount refunded accurately. </p>
            <h3>Does Republic Airways have access to Wi-Fi? </h3>
            <p>The flights of Republic Airways don't have any access to in-flight Wi-Fi. It means you'll have to face the network issue. </p>
